{"tid":2306460,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅志祥5億豪宅「偷蓋空中極樂游泳池」！　曾爆私約20大胸妹水裡玩","createTime":"2020-11-30T12:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T04:31:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc870bfb5ad598ad7ff423400f77a835822cefed","tid":2306460,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"羅志祥（小豬）4月經歷「毀滅性分手」，遭周揚青控訴「多人運動」後，不僅9年情斷，形象也受到重創，演藝工作全停擺，只偶爾分享日常生活。近日他被爆出打算在2年前購入的豪宅頂樓加蓋露天游泳池，引起住戶怨聲四起。<br />\n<br />\n羅志祥2013年在內湖買下2.7億元豪宅，把17樓2戶打通用來自住，2018年又買下同棟的23樓2戶打通，一度傳出是要用來當結婚新房，4戶價值近5億。據《自由時報》報導，近日卻爆他24及25樓中的頂樓加蓋空中露天游泳池，且已動工。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n物業管理公司得知後，立刻通知羅志祥停工，並表示需要事先申請，他稱加蓋泳池已經得到樓下住戶同意，但其實樓下也是他的房產，因而引起其他住戶不滿，他一度不滿打給物業公司抱怨，和其他單位開會後，最後決定暫時停工，對此，他的經紀人表示：「只是一般頂樓露台造景，都是遵守社區規定。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5304/d5304125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5304%2Fd5304125.jpg&h=a3f0c790&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n羅志祥4月被爆在宜蘭開趴，現場除了有好友大根（黃亮鈞），還傳出有近20名大胸妹一起狂歡，影片在網路上被瘋傳，影片中，可見小豬好友大根抱著一個熱褲辣妹從室內走到室外的泳池邊，穿著黑色運動裝的羅志祥則跟在後面，之後一起把辣妹推到池裡，玩得不亦樂乎，旁觀的人還爆出陣陣歡呼聲，畫面引起熱議。"},{"pid":"aff35a5c32f60dad6d71c64db0586e439b598116","tid":2306460,"uid":76804,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/proxy/WnpneFSRqCtpaRZpbOJf9hV0WUZBxgFMcx5X0IUCpHwU__URQrxKnuMqL2DOpdqjNo_b6n8ZfWGY7FZm7VZ74girj7OgXzOayBnq2RdUgi3313oVabY8dA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2Fproxy%2FWnpneFSRqCtpaRZpbOJf9hV0WUZBxgFMcx5X0IUCpHwU__URQrxKnuMqL2DOpdqjNo_b6n8ZfWGY7FZm7VZ74girj7OgXzOayBnq2RdUgi3313oVabY8dA&h=5c4c42e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水力發電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6f473e4928baad7f6beec1792c2fd2febcaebd","tid":2306460,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"瘋傳????????????"},{"pid":"f6b677133d2500a39a268976653a43fb10d702b5","tid":2306460,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:31:35.000Z","msg":"好羡慕小豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1648c7016f31973e29d0cb91d56bdd4b08a171cf","tid":2306460,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"無犯限聚令?"},{"pid":"8d89f621833f37d9242d264b4de81a9a83c40702","tid":2306460,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T12:32:50.000Z","msg":"20個大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2d688d49b814842dccaf9449faf1f8aed783f7","tid":2306460,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:11:57.000Z","msg":"又一個僭建聯成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c3476b41fa62e5d3597accc1fabf2e325e0470","tid":2306460,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:31:59.000Z","msg":"還傳出有近20名大胸妹一起狂歡，影片在網路上被瘋傳<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}